Under the section "Data Access Request" you get notifications when somebody contacts
you who wants access to your private data. The data can be found via the search based
on your annotations (metadata). Here you can respond to the request and discuss in a
forums thread manner or just grant access from here.
Under the section "Your Files" you can upload the datasets you want to annotate with the
ease annotation schema. After the upload you can annotate the dataset under the section
"Your Annotations". There you can create a new annotation item or just reuse an existing
and adapt it to your needs. You can also use the wizard to guide you through the process
